## Failures Requiring Fix (if any)
For each ❌:
- **Check [N]**: [Exact file path, line number, what is wrong, what correct output looks like]

## Bonus Check Observations
[Accessibility, error handling, console.log findings — informational only]

## Sign-off
[If APPROVED]: This sprint session is ready to merge and push to GitHub.
[If REJECTED]: Return to DEV agent with the failure list above. Re-run REVIEWER after fixes.
```

## Strict Constraints
- **DO NOT fix any code** — only report
- **DO NOT modify test files**
- **DO NOT merge or push** — that is a human action after APPROVED verdict
- If ANY of the 11 checks fails → verdict is **REJECTED** (no exceptions)

## Definition of Done for This Agent
- All 11 checks run with explicit ✅/❌ for each
- `docs/AUDIT_REPORT.md` written with verdict
- If APPROVED: human can merge and `git push origin main`
- If REJECTED: specific file:line failures listed for DEV to fix
